	If statements:
		- If else conditions allow us to write programs that can take decision bases on some condition and provided data.
		
		If condition
		if else condition
		if else if condition
		nested if else condition
		
	Why we should learn about if else condition?
		- When we are solving real life problems
		- Like testing a web site our program needs to make alot of decisions.
		
	What is the syntax of if else condition?
		-It condition:
		boolean rich=true;
			if (rich)
			{
